{"tid":1772092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解你地咁老定128一定可以上返100萬?","createTime":"2019-12-06T10:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T11:14:32.000Z","uid":283912,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ac8dd28996d8f5f0306d8cb97c6d3e8a29deba","tid":1772092,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"128唔好話200萬,上唔上得返100萬都危<br />\n<br />\n最主要原因:<br />\n近兩個月好多人覺得行動過激同事反文宣不吹<br />\n出黎和理非遊行成本提高,tg變基本盤<br />\n近一個月對家冇犯612,721,811之類大錯<br />\n區選+人權法後有人收咗貨<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日身邊好多行過616,818嘅人都話未必出<br />\n所以每人要盡量搵返200萬行過嘅出返黎<br />\n再拉多幾個冇行過嘅人一齊<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個非常緊要嘅族群:<br />\n就係呢幾個月藍/中立轉黃嘅人<br />\n連登好多po都見到好多巴絲父母成功染黃<br />\n128一定要帶哂佢地出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2b79c18c58b0769275f2dc62d72ad8e339d5a0","tid":1772092,"uid":314531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d669665712773f1f4cec1706a804c44c018a69fb","tid":1772092,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco